snippet.title: KINE: Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
A 3D puzzle game about machines with dreams of being musicians. Embark across a theatrically rendered cityscape solving increasingly difficult 3D puzzles. Help Euler, Quat, and Roo as they struggle to form a band and find their big break!

Add to your Steam Wishlist:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/824570/Kine/
